tspan.tspan: Supplementary Figure metadata ASD TD: Dietary and lifestyle differences between ASD and TD
individuals. The ending "freq" refers to a questionnaire query that asked about general habits.
Otherwise, questions were answered considering the week prior to sampling. P values from Wilcoxon
rank sum test reported. Whole grain, short and long term dairy, fruit, short and long term vegetable,
seafood, and starchy food consumption significantly differed between ASD and TD individuals.
